Author: Whose_cat_is_that
Text: I’m so addicted to them that for the few months I’ve been here, I’ve resorted to just drinking the regular version and then hating myself for it. I only found a small supply so far, but the packaging is local, and says it was made in shanghai, so I’m hoping it gets more widespread soon. I bought all the ones available in the store just in case though.

Author: SongstressVII
Text: I don’t think I would survive with Monster Zero Ultra or Rockstar Pure Zero. My coworkers say I’m fueled by caffeine and protein shakes. If only they knew how right they are...
